  "root_text": {
    "iti58:0.1": "Itivuttaka 58 ",
    "iti58:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti58:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti58:0.4": "Taṇhāsutta ",
    "iti58:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti58:2.1": "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, taṇhā. ",
    "iti58:2.2": "Katamā tisso? ",
    "iti58:2.3": "Kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā—",
    "iti58:2.4": "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso taṇhā”ti. ",
    "iti58:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti58:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti58:3.1": "“Taṇhāyogena saṁyuttā, ",
    "iti58:3.2": "rattacittā bhavābhave; ",
    "iti58:3.3": "Te yogayuttā mārassa, ",
    "iti58:3.4": "ayogakkhemino janā; ",
    "iti58:3.5": "Sattā gacchanti saṁsāraṁ, ",
    "iti58:3.6": "jātīmaraṇagāmino. ",
    "iti58:4.1": "Ye ca taṇhaṁ pahantvāna, ",
    "iti58:4.2": "vītataṇhā bhavābhave; ",
    "iti58:4.3": "Te ve pāraṅgatā loke, ",
    "iti58:4.4": "ye pattā āsavakkhayan”ti. ",
    "iti58:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti58:5.2": "Navamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti58:0.1": "So It Was Said 58 ",
    "iti58:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti58:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti58:0.4": "Craving ",
    "iti58:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti58:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three cravings. ",
    "iti58:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti58:2.3": "Craving for sensual pleasures, craving for existence, and craving for nonexistence. ",
    "iti58:2.4": "These are the three cravings.” ",
    "iti58:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti58:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti58:3.1": "“Bound by craving, minds full of desire ",
    "iti58:3.2": "for rebirth in this or that state, ",
    "iti58:3.3": "yoked by Māra’s yoke, these people ",
    "iti58:3.4": "find no sanctuary from the yoke. ",
    "iti58:3.5": "Sentient beings continue to transmigrate, ",
    "iti58:3.6": "with ongoing birth and death. ",
    "iti58:4.1": "Those who have given up craving, ",
    "iti58:4.2": "rid of craving for rebirth in this or that state, ",
    "iti58:4.3": "they in this world have truly crossed over, ",
    "iti58:4.4": "having reached the ending of defilements.” ",
    "iti58:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti58:2.1": "ve → te ca (bj, pts-vp-pli1, mr) | pāraṅgatā → pāragatā (sya-all) ",
    "iti58:3.6": "jātīmaraṇagāmino → jātimaraṇagāmino (bj, sya-all, pts-vp-pli1) ",
    "iti58:4.2": "vītataṇhā → nittaṇhā ca (si, mr) "
  },
